dct_title_s: Adelaide and South Australia / produced for and distributed by Hema Maps
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights on regional map. "Printed in Australia 1990." Panel title. Map shows 4 classes of roads, tracks, railways, and distances in kilometers. Includes index to towns.
